msgid "Keywords and Concepts"
msgstr "关键词和相关概念"

msgid "This is a list of keywords and rules on cards in this scenario to keep on hand while playing the game."
msgstr "以下是本场冒险中卡牌上的关键词与相关规则，在游戏时可以放在手边方便查看。"

msgid ""
"Doomed is a keyword ability.\n"
"When an enemy with the doomed keyword is defeated (either by an investigator or a scenario effect), place 1 doom on the current agenda. This effect can cause the current agenda to advance."
msgstr ""
"厄运降临时一个关键词能力。\n"
"在带有厄运降临关键词的敌人被（调查员或冒险效果）击败时，在当前密谋上放置1个毁灭标记。本效果能导致当前密谋推进。"

msgid "An effect that \"discards\" an enemy is not considered to defeat that enemy and does not trigger the doomed keyword."
msgstr "“弃掉”敌人的效果不视为击败了该敌人，不会触发厄运降临关键词。"

msgid ""
"Hunter is a keyword ability.\n"
"At the start of the enemy phase, each ready, unengaged enemy with the hunter keyword moves to a connecting location, along the shortest path towards the nearest investigator. Enemies at a location with one or more investigators do not move."
msgstr ""
"猎手是一个关键词能力。\n"
"当敌军阶段开始时，每个带有猎手关键词的敌人，若未与调查员交战，且处于重整状态，会沿着最短路线，向最近的调查员移动至一个连接地点。所在地点有调查员的敌人不会移动。"

msgid "Some enemies may target specific prey. (See \"Prey\" below.)"
msgstr "有些敌人会以特定的猎物作为对象。（见本页“猎物”）"

msgid "If there are multiple equidistant investigators who qualify as \"the nearest investigator,\" the hunter enemy moves towards the one who best meets its designated target. If none do, or if the enemy has no prey keyword, the lead investigator decides."
msgstr "如果有多位调查员距离相等，都为“最近的调查员”，则该敌人向最能满足其猎物指示的调查员移动。如果不能确定谁最能满足，或者该敌人没有猎物关键词，则由调查员队长决定。"

msgid "If a hunter enemy would be compelled to move into a location but is blocked by a card ability, that enemy does not move."
msgstr "如果带有猎手关键词的敌人将被强迫移动至一个地点，而该移动被卡牌能力阻断，则该敌人不移动。"

msgid ""
"Peril is a keyword ability.\n"
"While an investigator is resolving an encounter card with the peril keyword, they cannot confer with the other players. Other players cannot play cards, trigger abilities, or commit cards to that investigator's skill tests) while the peril encounter card is being resolved."
msgstr ""
"险境是一个关键词能力。\n"
"调查员结算带有险境关键词的遭遇卡牌时，不能与其他玩家交流。带有险境关键词的遭遇卡牌结算时，其他玩家不能打出卡牌、触发能力，也不能为正在结算的调查员的技能检定投入卡牌。"

msgid ""
"Prey is a keyword ability.\n"
"Given the opportunity, some enemies will pursue a defined investigator. These enemies are identified with the keyword Prey in their text box, followed by instructions on whom they should engage, in parentheses."
msgstr ""
"猎物是一个关键词能力。\n"
"若有机会，有些敌人会追猎特定的调查员。这样的敌人带有“猎物”关键词指示，后面括号内的文字说明其要与谁交战。"

msgid "Given the choice between multiple equidistant investigators (or between investigators at its location), an enemy with the prey keyword targets the investigator who best meets its prey instructions."
msgstr "在距离相等的多个调查员（或其所在地点的多个调查员）间选择时，带有猎物关键词的敌人会以最符合其标示的调查员作为对象。"

msgid ""
"Retaliate is a keyword ability.\n"
"Each time an investigator fails a skill test while attacking a ready enemy with the retaliate keyword, after applying all results for that skill test, that enemy performs an attack against the attacking investigator. An enemy does not exhaust after performing a retaliate attack."
msgstr ""
"反击是一个关键词能力。\n"
"调查员每次攻击带有反击关键词的敌人时，若敌人处于重整状态且调查员技能检定失败，在应用完该次检定的所有结果之后，该敌人对发起攻击的调查员执行一次攻击。敌人在执行反击攻击后不横置。"

msgid "This attack occurs whether or not the enemy is engaged with the attacking investigator."
msgstr "不论该敌人是否与进行攻击的调查员交战，这次攻击均会发生。"

msgid ""
"Surge is a keyword ability.\n"
"After an investigator draws and resolves an encounter card that has the surge keyword, that investigator must draw and resolve another card."
msgstr ""
"涌动是一个关键词能力。\n"
"调查员抽取并结算了带有涌动关键词的遭遇卡牌后，该调查员必须再抽取并结算另一张卡牌。"

msgid "If an investigator draws a card with the surge keyword during setup, the surge keyword still resolves."
msgstr "如果调查员在设置期间抽取了带有涌动关键词的卡牌，涌动关键词也会结算。"

msgid ""
"Some cards have the codex symbol ([codex]) on them. During a scenario, some card effects and abilities may direct players to read a specific codex entry. While playing, keep the campaign guide on hand for easy reference.\n"
"Certain locations, characters, and enemies have codex entries, marked with ([codex] X). To read a codex entry, pay all costs and/or resolve all effects associated with its triggering ability, then read the corresponding entry for the current scenario in the campaign guide and resolve its text."
msgstr ""
"有些卡牌上会带有抄本（[codex]）符号。在冒险期间，有些卡牌效果和能力会指示玩家阅读特定的抄本条目。玩家在游戏时应将剧本手册放在手边，以方便查阅。\n"
"特定的地点、角色和敌人会带有抄本条目，以（[codex]）标出。要阅读抄本条目，支付其所有费用和/或结算与其触发能力相关的所有效果，然后阅读剧本手册中当前冒险相应的条目，并结算其文本。"

msgid "When resolving a codex entry, the player who triggered that entry resolves all effects (resolving a test, dealing damage, paying resources, etc.). If it is unclear who triggered the codex entry, the lead investigator resolves the entry."
msgstr "在结算抄本条目时，由触发该条目的玩家结算其全部效果（结算检定、造成伤害、支付资源等）。如果无法确定是谁触发的抄本条目，则由调查员队长结算该条目。"

msgid "Codex entries that are triggered via a specific action type (such as <b>Fight</b>, <b>Evade</b>, <b>Parley</b>, etc.) are considered to be that action type throughout the resolution of that codex entry."
msgstr "由特定种类行动（例如<b>攻击</b>、<b>躲避</b>、<b>谈判</b>等）触发的抄本条目，结算过程中也视为该种行动。"

msgid "While resolving a codex entry, a player only reads the section for which they meet the requirements. If they do not meet the requirements to resolve the first section of a codex entry, skip to the following section."
msgstr "结算抄本条目时，玩家只能阅读达成需求的部分。如果没有达成某个抄本条目结算第一部分的需求，跳至下一部分。"

msgid "If a card effect directs players to resolve a codex entry that does not exist for the scenario being player, that effect fails."
msgstr "如果卡牌效果指示玩家结算的抄本条目并不存在于当前冒险，该效果失效。"

msgid "After resolving a codex entry and making any changes to the game and/or in the campaign log, resume play."
msgstr "结算抄本条目，更改游戏和/或剧本日志后，继续游戏。"

msgid ""
"Alert is a keyword ability.\n"
"Each time an investigator fails a skill test while attempting to evade a ready enemy with the alert keyword, after applying all results for that skill test, that enemy performs an attack against the evading investigator. An enemy does not exhaust after performing an alert attack."
msgstr ""
"警戒是一个关键词能力。\n"
"每当调查员在尝试躲避带有警戒关键词的敌人时技能检定失败，且该敌人为重整状态，在应用该技能检定带来的所有结果后，该敌人对尝试躲避的调查员执行一次攻击。敌人在执行警戒攻击后不横置。"

msgid "This attack occurs whether or not the enemy is engaged with the evading investigator."
msgstr "不论该敌人是否与进行躲避的调查员交战，这次攻击均会发生。"

msgid ""
"Aloof is a keyword ability.\n"
"An enemy with the aloof keyword does not automatically engage investigators at its location."
msgstr ""
"冷漠是一个关键词能力。\n"
"带有冷漠关键词的敌人，不会自动与所在地点的调查员交战。冷漠敌人在生成时不与调查员交战。"

msgid "When an aloof enemy spawns, it spawns unengaged."
msgstr "当一个冷漠的敌人生成时，它会以未交战状态生成。"

msgid "An investigator may use an engage action or a card ability to engage an aloof enemy."
msgstr "调查员可以使用交战行动或卡牌能力来与冷漠敌人交战。"

msgid "An investigator cannot attack or evade an aloof enemy while that enemy is not engaged with an investigator."
msgstr "冷漠敌人未与一位调查员交战时，调查员不能攻击或躲避该敌人。"

msgid ""
"Elusive is a keyword ability.\n"
"Elusive enemies represent enemies who want to avoid the investigators for their own survival or to accomplish their own goals. If a ready enemy with the elusive keyword attacks or is attacked, after that attack resolves, that enemy immediately disengages from all investigators, moves to a connecting location (with no investigators if able), and exhausts."
msgstr ""
"逃逸是一个关键词能力。\n"
"逃逸敌人宁愿避开调查员，只愿求存或者完成自己的目标。如果带有逃逸关键词的敌人攻击或受到攻击，且该敌人处于重整状态，则在该次攻击结算后，该敌人立即与所有调查员解除交战，移动到一个连接地点（如可能，移动到没有调查员的地点），并横置。"

msgid "This effect occurs whether or not the enemy was engaged with the attacking investigator."
msgstr "不论该敌人是否与进行攻击的调查员交战，该效果均会发生。"
